                                                                                                                        <li>
                                            <a href="https://i1.wp.com/www.burgessct.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/image.png?fit=1024%2C498&ssl=1" rel="prettyPhoto['gallery']"><img width="940" height="400" src="https://i1.wp.com/www.burgessct.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/image.png?resize=940%2C400&amp;ssl=1" class="attachment-portfolio-full size-portfolio-full wp-post-image" alt="burgessct - trump the termite in the white house" loading="lazy" /></a>                                    
